casebody.data:
State of North Carolina
v.
Robert Antwain Stanback No. 135P16 Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 9, 2016 Alexander McC. Peters, Special Deputy Attorney General, Garland N. Yates, District Attorney, For State of North Carolina. Robert A. Stanback, Pro Per.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 14th of April 2016 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Randolph County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 9th of June 2016."

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 14th of April 2016 by Defendant to Appoint Counsel:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference, this the 9th of June 2016."
